# 2. Key Capabilities

### ✔ Structural Polarity (POS / NEG / NON)
- **Preciencia (POS)** → coherent structural pattern  
- **Inverted / Simulacrum (NEG)** → pattern that breaks proportion or mechanism  
- **Non-Structured (NON)** → surreal, floating, or non-anchored pattern  
- **Structural Ally** → symbolic override when structure is present but v5 misfires

### ✔ Engine v4 — Coherence Metrics  
- **C** (coherence cost)  
- **coherence_score = exp(−C)**  
- **S_sim** (cycle similarity)  
- **θ_check** (invariance threshold pass/fail)

### ✔ Macro-Field Mapping (v6b)
Maps text into one of 12 symbolic/topological fields.

### ✔ Symbolic Layer v2 (Explainable Rules)
